law.history: Repealed 2004 Ky. Acts ch 189, sec. 31, effective July 13, 2004. -- Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 63, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1988. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 39, sec. 1, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 119, sec. 30, effective June 17, 1954.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Liability for property loss or injury by dog or coyote -- Procedures for enforcing claims for damages.
